56
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:09,960
It's such a huge piece.

57
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:11,840
Have some tea.

58
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,680
Okay.

59
00:04:14,150 --> 00:04:15,280
Just look at the tea cup.

60
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:18,510
It has a crystal-clear warmth
and a rouge-like purple tint to it.

61
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,240
Don't tell me

62
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,360
it's a piece of Jun Kiln.

63
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,000
Really?

64
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,560
How could you use this for tea?

65
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,950
