66
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:33,790
you know?

67
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,750
Mr. Bi,

68
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:38,830
to be honest with you,

69
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:39,670
I do have

70
00:04:39,870 --> 00:04:41,560
a tiny collection as well.

71
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,870
If you have the time,

72
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,190
please check them out

73
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:45,240
