I shouldn't trouble you.

77
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:53,560
I should bring them here
and show them to you instead.

78
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:54,710
What about this?

79
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,920
I'll go and get them right now.

80
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,240
Please wait for me.

81
