are a good fit for me.

111
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,680
You know?

112
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,510
But Market Lord, why do I feel like

113
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:28,560
your face has become more rounded?

114
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,520
Don't you agree?

115
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:32,270
Who said so?

116
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:34,710
Isn't that the case?

117
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:37,560
Why would you grow rounder
if you didn't have an appetite?

118
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,200
A face as round as a silver plate

119
00:06:39,210 --> 00:06:40,240
will serve to
demonstrate one's prosperity.

120
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,680
Shut up if you don't know what to say.

121
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,240
I don't like them! I'm not taking them!

122
00:06:45,630 --> 00:06:47,190
It was just a joke.

123
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,560
Why are you so petty?

124
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,830
Of course I understood
what you meant, Market Lord.

125
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,810
I already prepared
something else in advance.

126
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,960
Su Beilu.

127
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:57,030
Coming.

128
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,360
I just happened to bring four cups.

129
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,510
One for each of us.

130
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,560
Aren't you...

131
00:07:03,310 --> 00:07:04,480
What are you doing here?

132
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:05,910
Chu Qiu,

133
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,720
is anyone allowed
to enter Luoxia Manor now?

134
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:12,120
Not if they're empty-handed.

135
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,650
That's right.

136
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:15,510
I came here to bring you
some boba milk tea.

137
00:07:15,510 --> 00:07:17,970
It's a popular beverage in our era.
They sell this everywhere.

138
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,920
And, this shop sells the best boba.

139
00:07:21,190 --> 00:07:22,030
Hurry and try it.

140
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:24,590
You think you can brush me off
with such an ordinary beverage?

141
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,040
I'll take it if you don't want it.

142
00:07:27,060 --> 00:07:29,470
Since you've gone through
all the effort to bring this here,

143
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,360
I... I suppose I can give it a try.

144
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,440
Wait.

145
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,120
I have to test any food
that's brought here

146
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:41,040
