Market Lord tries them.

147
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:47,880
How is it?

148
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,320
Wait a little longer.

149
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,240
Are you done?

150
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:02,430
The onset of toxin takes time.

151
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,830
Just tell us directly if you want one.

152
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:07,190
Don't leave Market Lord hanging.

153
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:08,870
Just drink it. I wouldn't poison you.

154
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:09,750
Precisely.

155
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:16,000
It's so delicious.

156
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:18,510
This is called
Glutinous Bubble Milk Foam

157
00:08:18,510 --> 00:08:21,040
Popping Tea with Sesame,
Berry, Mango, and Peach.

158
00:08:25,300 --> 00:08:26,990
