160
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:31,390
Glutinous Bubble Milk Foam Popping Tea
with Sesame, Berry, Mango, and Peach.

161
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,910
Glutinous...

162
00:08:36,030 --> 00:08:36,960
Popping...

163
00:08:38,140 --> 00:08:39,200
I can't remember the name.

164
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,670
It's delicious. Let's have a toast.

165
00:08:40,670 --> 00:08:41,760
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

166
00:08:43,570 --> 00:08:46,200
Market Lord, since you've enjoyed
the delicious drink we brought,

167
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,040
if so,

168
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:49,120
about the item we desire...

169
00:08:50,140 --> 00:08:51,120
I almost forgot about it.

170
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,270
Thank you, Market Lord.

171
00:08:55,550 --> 00:08:56,840
Repeat the name.

172
