240
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,310
A mermaid?

241
00:17:36,350 --> 00:17:37,200
Young girl,

242
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:39,030
why were you crying

243
00:17:39,550 --> 00:17:41,030
