623
00:39:26,540 --> 00:39:27,380
Miss.

624
00:39:30,980 --> 00:39:31,820
Mr. Jiang Ling?

625
00:39:36,580 --> 00:39:37,580
I didn't expect

626
00:39:37,580 --> 00:39:38,900
to see you again today.

627
00:39:39,420 --> 00:39:40,700
I suppose we're destined to meet.

628
00:39:42,820 --> 00:39:44,140
You look pale.

629
00:39:44,140 --> 00:39:45,500
Are you sick?

630
00:39:46,340 --> 00:39:47,180
That's not it.

631
00:39:47,980 --> 00:39:48,860
I'm glad to hear that.

632
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:51,740
Next time, you must be careful
when you walk alone at night.

633
00:39:52,340 --> 00:39:55,500
I heard that they found someone dead
by the lakeside last night.

634
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:56,460
And, it was an official.

635
00:39:58,660 --> 00:39:59,740
Is that so?

636
00:40:00,740 --> 00:40:03,320
Next time, when you walk alone at night,
you can tell me about it.

637
00:40:03,620 --> 00:40:05,420
My guard can escort you home.

638
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:09,260
Thank you, Mr. Jiang Ling.

639
00:40:11,260 --> 00:40:12,100
Farewell.

640
00:40:13,340 --> 00:40:14,180
Wait.

641
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:18,300
Mr. Jiang Ling,
I haven't repaid your favor yet.

642
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:20,720
Although these scented sachets
are nothing precious,

643
00:40:20,740 --> 00:40:22,020
please take some of them.

644
00:40:28,090 --> 00:40:30,340
Mr. Jiang Ling, I'm sure
you're used to exquisite wares.

645
00:40:30,860 --> 00:40:32,940
My needlework is rather clumsy.

646
00:40:33,540 --> 00:40:35,420
I hope you don't mind.

647
00:40:36,420 --> 00:40:38,220
"A red ribbon
and a brocade scented sachet,

648
00:40:38,380 --> 00:40:39,820
given to show my affection to you,

649
00:40:40,300 --> 00:40:41,460
dear young sir".

650
00:40:43,860 --> 00:40:46,540
I heard that one buys scented sachets
for the people they fancy.

651
00:40:53,260 --> 00:40:54,620
Your needlework is exquisite.

652
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:56,500
And, the scent is unique.

653
00:40:56,820 --> 00:40:57,860
What kind of scent is this?

654
00:40:58,120 --> 00:41:00,400
I made this scent from
the flowers growing in my backyard.

655
00:41:01,780 --> 00:41:04,340
They're merely cheap wildflowers.

656
00:41:04,640 --> 00:41:06,060
There's only one person in my heart.

657
00:41:06,500 --> 00:41:08,420
Therefore, I only need
one scented sachet.

658
00:41:11,780 --> 00:41:12,620
Here you go.

659
00:41:13,220 --> 00:41:14,260
Mister, you don't have to.

660
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:15,380
It's a gift from me.

661
00:41:15,820 --> 00:41:16,660
Just take it.

662
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:20,940
Thank you, Mr. Jiang Ling.

663
00:41:23,340 --> 00:41:26,180
By the way, I haven't had the pleasure
of learning your name yet.

664
00:41:26,380 --> 00:41:27,340
I'm Chan.

665
00:41:27,620 --> 00:41:28,460
Chan?

666
00:41:30,300 --> 00:41:31,140
Chan.

667
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:34,380
Tomorrow night, there will be
a poetry gathering by Lake Dongting.

668
00:41:34,580 --> 00:41:36,220
I'm the organizer.

669
00:41:36,420 --> 00:41:38,060
Chan, I hope you can make it.

670
00:41:40,500 --> 00:41:42,700
When you're there,
just show them this scented sachet.

671
00:41:42,900 --> 00:41:44,180
They'll allow you to go upstairs.

672
00:41:51,520 --> 00:41:52,580
I shall make a move first.

